WEBVTT

00:03.600 --> 00:08.915
I believe you all say these things,

00:13.278 --> 00:15.278
and you listen to it,

00:25.269 --> 00:27.269
and you say it from your heart.

00:30.449 --> 00:36.673
Only the one who are united with God can worship Shri Ganesha.

00:40.920 --> 00:42.920
And Shri Ganesha worships your Mother.

00:57.510 --> 00:59.510
First of all

01:01.421 --> 01:03.421
one must to understand

01:06.037 --> 01:09.034
that there is a combination of a Mother and a Guru.

01:12.484 --> 01:14.484
Because Guru is a very hard task master.

01:17.260 --> 01:19.260
He does not allow any liberties to be taken.

01:22.325 --> 01:24.325
And Mother is very kindly.

01:30.724 --> 01:34.245
But you don't have feelings for the Mother, do you?

01:47.955 --> 01:50.781
Is it all a lip-service that you listen,

01:51.281 --> 01:54.792
goes into your head, and you think you have become

01:56.510 --> 01:58.870
the surrendered Sahaja yogis?

02:00.364 --> 02:04.271
Like all Islam people believe they are surrendered to God,

02:04.322 --> 02:07.322
like Christians believe they are surrendered to God.

02:08.656 --> 02:12.103
It's just a lip-service that you are this, you are that.

02:13.082 --> 02:17.858
Or do you know it him, what is said, is a fact.

02:21.436 --> 02:23.695
Have you not seen the Sun in my hand?

02:24.868 --> 02:26.517
What more proof you want?

02:48.552 --> 02:53.166
Anybody who misleads you is of course sinful no doubt,

02:55.409 --> 02:57.824
but to fall a trap to such a person!

03:01.035 --> 03:05.247
If you had told a child that the Mother is coming, he would have fought,

03:05.747 --> 03:06.534
"I'm going".

03:09.994 --> 03:11.994
He would have cried and wept.

03:16.976 --> 03:18.976
What about your vibrations?

03:20.195 --> 03:22.195
You don't use your vibrations?

03:23.940 --> 03:26.770
You have come all the way for Guru Puja here,

03:27.381 --> 03:30.143
who is your Guru? Whom are you going to worship?

03:31.777 --> 03:36.217
Anybody comes from anywhere becomes suddenly important. How?

03:43.440 --> 03:45.440
It was never done before,

03:46.327 --> 03:48.994
first time I see such a horrible thing.

03:51.514 --> 03:55.445
In my living time if you are doing like this, after my death so many gurus will rise,

03:56.402 --> 03:57.087
to mislead you.

04:05.389 --> 04:07.389
Are you going to accept all that?

04:27.007 --> 04:31.727
All the Deities refused for me to do this.

04:31.923 --> 04:35.482
They tortured my life, they would not accept

04:36.540 --> 04:41.139
to allow you to have the Puja. Absolutely, nothing doing.

04:46.093 --> 04:48.684
Because they love me, they respect me.

04:49.184 --> 04:51.184
They have the proper protocol.

04:51.241 --> 04:53.241
They don't want to become gurus themselves,

04:53.741 --> 04:55.741
and misbehave in this manner.

05:11.956 --> 05:18.141
Last time when I came I really was very strong, with the French.

05:21.435 --> 05:27.565
I've told so many times that France is the Hell of the Universe.

05:34.539 --> 05:38.465
And you should fall a trap to something like that?

05:39.076 --> 05:43.207
It's very supra-conscious, extremely supra-conscious.

05:44.744 --> 05:45.762
And arrogant.

05:56.997 --> 06:00.897
I've never known of such a Guru Puja. Never.

06:02.448 --> 06:05.595
Indians had only one Guru Puja, and they are praying that

06:05.901 --> 06:08.682
they should have at least one more Guru Puja.

06:10.012 --> 06:13.580
With all these Guru Pujas if you have achieved this kind of surrendering,

06:14.135 --> 06:16.871
it's better you do not have any more Guru Pujas at all.

06:17.371 --> 06:20.154
Don't deserve it. You cannot become Gurus,

06:20.654 --> 06:21.924
I can see that clearly.

06:23.420 --> 06:25.420
Without surrender how will you?

06:59.564 --> 07:02.931
All the Blessings of the Divine

07:04.870 --> 07:06.096
have been showered upon you.

07:08.892 --> 07:10.892
And what have you given back?

07:16.787 --> 07:18.787
Such ego?

07:19.287 --> 07:22.538
That you act to somebody because he has greater egos?

07:42.211 --> 07:44.211
It is a very bad example.

07:51.296 --> 07:55.031
You have to wash the feet of the Indians and drink that water.

07:55.531 --> 07:58.659
May be then you might realize where you are.

07:59.353 --> 08:01.353
You may be very developed and all that.

08:02.572 --> 08:04.572
And the Indians who are of your type,

08:06.151 --> 08:08.151
all of them have to do that.

08:16.204 --> 08:18.204
Why didn't you see your vibrations?

08:21.028 --> 08:24.848
When the blind gets his eyes, he doesn't close his eyes to see things, does he?

08:29.498 --> 08:31.498
And what has happened to your leaders also?

08:40.039 --> 08:42.039
All of them put together could not

08:42.111 --> 08:44.539
say that we will not have this nonsense at this time?

08:55.542 --> 08:59.700
Just coming to the airport, so many people have risen higher in life.

09:00.695 --> 09:01.930
What are you doing here?

09:08.529 --> 09:10.529
You should have protested.

09:13.431 --> 09:17.057
I would like to know how many wanted to go to the airport and asked for it.

09:17.157 --> 09:19.277
Raise your hands. Honestly.

09:22.367 --> 09:23.234
Honestly.

09:35.178 --> 09:37.178
These are the only people who love me.

09:41.418 --> 09:42.304
May God Bless you.

10:02.909 --> 10:05.993
Tomorrow somebody tells you to insult me, will you do that?

10:17.183 --> 10:21.567
You know that if a king arrives from a small little place somewhere,

10:23.292 --> 10:26.651
or a prime minister from a very small island,

10:31.470 --> 10:33.602
from lardy and muddy island

10:34.102 --> 10:35.304
the prime minister came,

10:36.118 --> 10:39.907
and the prime minister of England had to go receive him.

10:49.177 --> 10:50.824
And if your Guru has come,

10:50.927 --> 10:52.927
all the gurus have to come to receive me,

10:55.529 --> 10:57.679
or to listen to something nonsensical here?

11:01.786 --> 11:04.846
I felt like going back from the airport only,

11:05.346 --> 11:07.346
the kind of vibrations I felt.

11:12.943 --> 11:14.943
How do you get into this kind of a maya?

11:19.183 --> 11:22.346
How you join hands? Except for a few.

11:32.411 --> 11:34.411
“Your quality will be known:

11:36.417 --> 11:39.146
how much you are surrendered to Me".

11:40.440 --> 11:41.552
Christ has said that.

11:47.099 --> 11:48.830
And today I say to you that.

11:52.491 --> 11:55.058
On all other things Sahaja yogis will protest.

11:56.121 --> 11:58.951
"This was not good, that was not good, this was done”.

11:59.069 --> 12:01.517
Against each other, against everything they will protest.

12:07.759 --> 12:10.094
"Sahaja yogi took this much money from us, and

12:10.131 --> 12:12.131
this should not have happened," they always tell me.

12:12.168 --> 12:14.901
Complaints and complaints, and complaints, and complaints!

12:21.723 --> 12:25.814
And for this kind of a nonsense they have no protest, nothing!

12:36.855 --> 12:39.202
You are all ego-oriented people and you like

12:39.421 --> 12:41.421
egoistical supra-conscious nonsense.

12:41.441 --> 12:42.790
That's what it is.

12:51.730 --> 12:54.193
You have all come for Guru Puja or for what have you come for?

12:55.424 --> 12:56.448
It is beyond me.

13:02.122 --> 13:05.363
This I'm talking to you as your Mother, and not as your Guru.

13:08.246 --> 13:09.880
As a Guru I’ll do what I have to do.

13:12.581 --> 13:15.446
I'm talking to you as a Mother. Is this the way to respect Her?

13:20.266 --> 13:23.165
I told you, this is the last Guru Puja you'll be having,

13:23.270 --> 13:26.004
the last Puja you will be having, perhaps may be.

13:34.736 --> 13:36.736
It's shocking!

13:48.158 --> 13:50.158
You have to respect your Guru.

13:50.476 --> 13:51.788
Surrender to your Guru.

13:53.182 --> 13:55.347
It is said that the Guru is

13:55.384 --> 13:59.070
the Param Chaitanya, but it is: the Param Chaitanya itself is your Guru.

14:05.685 --> 14:11.159
"Agata Parama Chaitanya, Dhanyoham Tava Dharshan -

14:12.756 --> 14:15.859
When the Paramchaitanya itself will come on this earth,

14:16.623 --> 14:18.539
I will feel myself so gratified

14:18.609 --> 14:20.958
to see the darshan of that Maya.

14:23.808 --> 14:25.808
In what world are you living?

14:26.308 --> 14:27.277
Where are you?

14:30.408 --> 14:31.371
Taking for granted?

14:41.270 --> 14:44.010
I know Mother has a right to punish you, very well.

14:44.510 --> 14:46.939
Even Krishna could be punished by His Mother.

14:53.992 --> 14:55.231
But I'm not interested.

15:01.308 --> 15:03.441
The children who want to disrespect me,

15:03.577 --> 15:05.577
and insult me, I have nothing to do with them.

15:09.271 --> 15:11.271
They have no love for me, I have nothing to do.

15:19.135 --> 15:20.057
Only those

15:20.838 --> 15:24.517
who protested and wanted to go to the airport should come forward to do my Puja.

15:28.757 --> 15:29.752
Honestly.

15:38.807 --> 15:40.379
You should be ashamed of yourself.

15:44.404 --> 15:47.220
You have insulted your Mother, who has given you Realization,

15:48.680 --> 15:51.157
who has done so much for you. Selflessly I've been working

15:52.203 --> 15:53.053
day in and day out,

15:58.319 --> 16:01.301
neglecting my own children, my own family,

16:02.827 --> 16:03.769
my grandchildren.

16:04.269 --> 16:05.294
For you?

16:27.820 --> 16:30.995
Only those people who wanted to go to the airport

16:31.495 --> 16:34.078
and said, and did not go, please come forward.

16:36.415 --> 16:36.912
Please.

16:52.305 --> 16:52.745
Come.

17:02.363 --> 17:04.363
He is meeting Me after so many years.

17:06.187 --> 17:07.037
When did you come?

17:10.913 --> 17:11.797
Just imagine,

17:12.247 --> 17:14.565
they come all the way from here and there, and there.

17:14.833 --> 17:17.399
And nicely you are telling them to listen to some nonsense?

17:18.346 --> 17:20.763
They have not come here to listen to anybody’s nonsense.

17:34.039 --> 17:36.039
Come forward, this side.

17:38.856 --> 17:41.735
Yes, of course, those who could not come,

17:41.788 --> 17:43.788
because they arrived late, I told them

17:44.040 --> 17:45.319
there is no program in the evening.

17:48.516 --> 17:49.490
All the Spanish,

17:50.685 --> 17:51.666
