21:01.914 --> 21:05.272
I will also forgive Austrians, because their leader wanted to go.

21:06.732 --> 21:08.732
Austrians should be forgiven,

21:09.381 --> 21:11.381
because their leader wanted to go.

21:13.619 --> 21:15.619
They could come up too.

21:24.575 --> 21:27.273
One man can save and one man can destroy.

21:30.487 --> 21:32.801
Your leader is alright till it comes to Mother's point,

21:33.301 --> 21:35.301
but when you reach that point,

21:37.390 --> 21:39.390
then, you have to protest against your leader.

21:45.285 --> 21:47.088
Come along, come, sit here.

21:47.191 --> 21:48.560
All the rest should go at the back,

21:50.285 --> 21:51.319
just go at the back.

21:54.285 --> 21:58.447
Please go back. All others, go back,

22:00.734 --> 22:01.725
and sit down there.

22:06.263 --> 22:10.328
I had to promise this. I had to promise this to the Deities.

22:22.560 --> 22:24.560
They would not accept, they would not accept!

22:33.168 --> 22:36.442
You must know there are Deities and Ganas and everyone is sitting here.

22:36.479 --> 22:39.805
They came forward before me, to France.

22:49.092 --> 22:51.624
24 hours they are working, you know that very well.

22:51.677 --> 22:53.677
You know it, it's not a story. You know that.

22:54.326 --> 22:57.724
They are working for you, helping you in every way, solving all your problems,

22:58.075 --> 22:58.547
don't they?

