23:10.136 --> 23:11.322
Because he should have said that.

23:11.640 --> 23:12.568
So Gavin should go back.

23:14.409 --> 23:16.263
And all the English, who came here early,

23:16.472 --> 23:18.750
just to attend everything, to attend what, the nonsense?

23:23.151 --> 23:25.516
Gavin said he did not know, there was going to be a lecture

23:25.524 --> 23:26.816
otherwise he would of object it.

23:27.048 --> 23:28.668
But what about coming to the airport_

23:36.177 --> 23:38.177
English know how much I have worked with them.

23:45.474 --> 23:48.110
All the leaders who did not protest should also go back.

23:56.134 --> 23:57.241
All should go.

23:58.290 --> 23:59.898
Those who have not protested.

24:14.181 --> 24:15.267
Guido you protested?

24:16.305 --> 24:18.337
Yes, Italians could be there.

24:25.192 --> 24:26.406
Guido protested,

24:26.634 --> 24:29.895
he could not understand: what was happening? Where is our Mother?

24:32.904 --> 24:35.936
Come this side. All the rest go at the back.

24:40.691 --> 24:42.775
What courage is needed for that kind of a thing?

24:50.991 --> 24:51.744
Of course.

24:58.399 --> 25:00.413
Otherwise there is a protest for everything,

25:00.658 --> 25:02.658
every day I'm receiving letters from people:

25:04.378 --> 25:06.921
"This is not good, that is not working out in Australia,

25:06.928 --> 25:09.079
is not working out here, that is not happening”.

25:09.380 --> 25:11.370
Everybody has a right to criticize everyone.

25:47.182 --> 25:50.545
French have been stupid in the past, and they are stupid even now.

25:51.492 --> 25:52.153
That's what they are,

25:53.090 --> 25:54.196
think knowing no end of themselves.

25:55.299 --> 25:57.775
Spanish people were, once upon a time, very aggressive,

25:58.056 --> 26:00.056
but in Sahaja Yoga they are not like that.

26:05.230 --> 26:07.230
You must learn how to respect.

26:13.061 --> 26:14.638
You've had no good training.

26:15.138 --> 26:17.910
“Very bad breeding” - that's what God is going to say about you.

26:21.861 --> 26:23.973
I've done my level best to tell you how to behave.

26:41.581 --> 26:43.947
No protocol, any sense of protocol you have.

26:46.072 --> 26:47.075
It's like beggars.

26:59.881 --> 27:01.881
Today you have to resolve,

27:04.955 --> 27:06.955
and ask the forgiveness of all the Deities,

27:08.423 --> 27:12.744
that you are going to use your vibrations all the time. Resolve.

27:14.869 --> 27:18.909
And that no more such a thing we are going to repeat again. This is the last,

27:19.938 --> 27:20.695
never like this.

27:21.524 --> 27:23.787
I am very suppressed that English,

27:23.794 --> 27:26.686
they come even in sleet, in snow, this, that.

27:26.857 --> 27:29.729
And here what happened, as soon as they came to hell they became hellish?

27:31.179 --> 27:33.179
What have happen to the English?

27:39.065 --> 27:41.065
They have no personality of their own?

27:42.533 --> 27:46.155
Always they followed the French, and now go with them to the ditch.

27:46.655 --> 27:49.150
